com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views

Class EntityView

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.EntityView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.ui.Model
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityFormView, EntityListView

    public class EntityView
extends Object
implements org.springframework.ui.Model
    Uses a backing ModelMap for storing and fetching the different attributes. Has a getTemplate() method that refers to the rendering template; as such it can be seen as an alternative to ModelAndView without putting dependencies on Spring mvc.

    The backing model can be (partially) prefilled and passed in externally. Default SimpleEntityViewFactorySupport implementations use the model as communication channel for data attributes between preparation and creation steps of a EntityView.

    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    SimpleEntityViewFactorySupport
